{"tid":2045980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人明住大西北既感受？","createTime":"2020-06-01T06:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T07:21:45.000Z","uid":140912,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c92c73311c5eb3cd4d495e6f9fe282a8f404b1d9","tid":2045980,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"望到隔離長途返工嘅post，有好深感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n住屯元天既去邊都一個鐘咁<br />\n日日要過海返工既，諗到屯門公路已經眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先唔講車錢，收工既時候屯公周不時塞車塞到喊，有位坐叫好D，冇位既企返個零兩個鐘頭正常事。仲要記得唔好飲水，如果唔係加埋你急屎急尿真係令你生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時放假真係寧願喺屋企休息下都唔想同朋友出去，唔知大家有冇發現一樣嘢， 就係住大西北嘅人永遠都係要出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有次同個朋友講起不如你入嚟，佢即刻話我痴線有病high撚大左，話要成個鐘先入到黎好撚遠唔入。 <br />\n<br />\n唉。其實你哋有冇諗過，我哋每次出嚟又何嘗唔係成個鐘？但我哋從來都冇資格出聲，好似住大西北就一定要我哋出去咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如試下搵次就返我地一次咁大把，唔洗騎牛唔洗passport都入到嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be779df4bb1687b6932aea3de7825266f753965e","tid":2045980,"uid":162095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:31:10.000Z","msg":"同同事講返工要一個鐘頭左右<br />\n佢好驚訝咁講好難想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf4f3d39982768836351a609d80fa4889a6cbf5","tid":2045980,"uid":31690,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:31:11.000Z","msg":"鬼叫窮住大西北咩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15946d08520d8fe80aed7a483315c5431594c36a","tid":2045980,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"好羨慕人哋一落樓下行三兩分鐘就可以返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3e422fbc286e354a1098ac573c09b2ed855f71","tid":2045980,"uid":5995,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:32:29.000Z","msg":"點解唔係大西北搵工？"},{"pid":"4527180713114d1576f915320d4733d65bff7167","tid":2045980,"uid":180652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:33:43.000Z","msg":"可以推介下d朋友入黎體驗下搭輕鐵。<br />\n刺激過過山車，唔L洗去海洋公園"},{"pid":"c7dc4d3c503bc39de6a02a445c546055abb5663e","tid":2045980,"uid":11699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:35:15.000Z","msg":"搬撚咗幾年，心情好返唔少，人都健康返"},{"pid":"3185486c3cef2c8900a84740f595dff459f1724d","tid":2045980,"uid":140912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bf4f3d39982768836351a609d80fa4889a6cbf5","tid":2045980,"uid":31690,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:31:11.000Z","msg":"鬼叫窮住大西北咩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:35:37.000Z","msg":"好似住大西北就係錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當聽到朋友話入嚟係一個鐘痴撚線嘅時候<br />\n我想講我每次出黎同佢食餐飯食一個鐘<br />\n但來回要用2個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢撘鐵來回半個鐘都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18454da7fdf4ad413483e877692d1c0c0a41ad68","tid":2045980,"uid":34759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c92c73311c5eb3cd4d495e6f9fe282a8f404b1d9","tid":2045980,"uid":140912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"r